{"type":"answer","id":28802,"parentType":"question","parentId":5411,"uid":6965,"contents":"这个事吧，要是说别的什么生态问题或者其他问题我可能会信，说它变形然后拿出其他什么有说服力的证据我也可能会信，然而这个卫星图实在是很难说有什么说服力...<br>\n<br>\n这是紧挨着的大堤和旁边的两栋建筑，扭曲应该是很明显的。而且这些都比大坝短很多，大坝那么长扭曲肯定更为严重。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pic3.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d178065026.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic3.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d178065026.png\" alt=\"https://pic3.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d178065026.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pic.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d178065029.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d178065029.png\" alt=\"https://pic.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d178065029.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://pic.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d17806502d.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d17806502d.png\" alt=\"https://pic.superbed.cn/item/5d23e8e1451253d17806502d.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-07-09","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}